Class SummaryListener

java.lang.Object
net.i2p.router.web.SummaryListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
RateSummaryListener
public class SummaryListener extends Object implements RateSummaryListener
Creates and updates the in-memory or on-disk RRD database, and provides methods to generate graphs of the data
